# 🚀 Lead Automation (Google Sheets → Gmail)

## 📌 Overview
This workflow automates lead response using n8n.

When a new lead is added to Google Sheets, an email is automatically sent using Gmail.

---

## ⚙️ Tools Used
- n8n
- Google Sheets
- Gmail

---

## 🔄 Workflow Logic
1. Trigger: New row added in Google Sheets  
2. Extract data (Name, Email, Phone, Service)  
3. Send personalized email via Gmail  

---

## ✉️ Example Email
Subject: Thanks {{Name}}!

Body:
Hello {{Name}},  
Thank you for your interest in {{Service}}. We will contact you soon.

